headline.print_headline: Alabama Republicans Say Voter Fraud Found After Offering Reward
headline.main: Alabama Republicans Say Voter Fraud Found After Offering Reward

lead_paragraph: Alabama Republicans, who offered a $1,000 reward for substantiated reports of voter fraud in this month's primary elections, said on Thursday they plan to forward credible evidence of wrongdoing to state prosecutors.
